Package fr.istic.aco.editor.Interface

Interface Command

All Known Subinterfaces:
CommandOriginator
All Known Implementing Classes:
CopyCommand, CutCommand, DeleteCommand, InsertCommand, PasteCommand, ReplayCommand, SelectionCommand, StartCommand, StopCommand
public interface Command
The Command interface defines the structure for all commands in the editor. Implementing classes must provide an implementation for the execute method, which performs the associated action.

    Method

    execute()

    • execute

      void execute()
      Executes the command's action. This method must be implemented by all concrete command classes.
